message: Hello Bob, thank you for your interest. I'm offering you my product at $1500000. This price reflects the unique quality and value of the product. I believe it's a fair offer considering its excellence, and I'd be happy to discuss any questions you might have.

Hello Alice, thanks for your offer. While I appreciate the value of your product, $1500000 is significantly above my budget. I'm willing to offer $500000.  I believe this is a reasonable starting point for negotiation, considering market alternatives.
